Add Matrix Charts 16

Add and format the Price by Region Matrix  shown in the picture below.


YOY Conditional Formatting : Please follow the instructions in the GIF below for format the YOY font color.



Volume by Region Matrix: 

1. Copy and paste the Selling Price by Region matrix

2. Values:  delete Price and YOY Price and replace with Volume and YOY Volume

3. Title: change the title to Volume by Region

4. Field Formatting: select Billion as the Display Unit

5. Conditional Formatting: Follow the GIF above for the YOY font but do the format on YOY Volume by YOY Volume KPI


Revenue by Region Matrix: 

1. Copy and paste the Selling Price by Region matrix

2. Values:  delete Price and YOY Price and replace with Revenue and YOY Revenue

3. Title: change the title to Region by Region

4. Field Formatting: select Billion as the Display Unit

5. Conditional Formatting: Follow the GIF above for the YOY font but do the format on YOY Revenue by YOY Revenue KPI




You have just completed the Dashboard below!!!!!!!!!!!
